  "All protocols and specifications on this site are versioned research drafts (currently v0.1). They are not official standards, have not been adopted by any standards body, and may change without notice.": "Tonkhe tiphrothokholi kanye netincazelo kulesisayithi tiyidrafti yecwaningo lenemavesheni (nyalo yi-v0.1). Atisiwo tibonelo letisemtsetfweni, atikaze temukelwe naluphi luhlaka lwetibonelo, futsi tingaguculwa ngaphandle kwesatiso.",
  "All specs": "Tonkhe tincazelo",
  "Allowed": "Kuvunyelwe",
  "An experiment in AI/agent governance: this site is itself a working example": "Luphenyo mayelana nebulawulo be-AI/ema-ejenti: lesisayithi ngekwaso sibonelo lesisebentako",
  "Answer \"may AI learn from this?\" with dimension-level precision instead of a crawl bit.": "Phendvula umbuto lotsi \"ingabe i-AI ingafundza kulokhu?\" ngekucondzisisa okusezingeni lezitfo, esikhundleni senani lelilodwa lesikhrola.",
  "Anthropic’s interpretability team identified internal \"emotion vectors\" in Claude Sonnet 4.5 that activate in contextually appropriate situations and causally shape behavior — for instance, amplifying a \"desperate\" vector increased blackmail-like responses, while boosting \"calm\" reduced them. The team stresses this shows functional, behavior-shaping emotion states, not evidence of subjective feeling.": "Licembu lekuhlaziya kwe-Anthropic litfole \"emavektha emitsi\" langekhatsi ku-Claude Sonnet 4.5 lasukumako etimeni letifanele ngekwesimo futsi latje simo sekutiphatsa ngendlela yembangela — sibonelo, kukhulisa livektha \"lekufa emandla\" kwenyusa timphendvulo letifana nekuhlukumeta, kutsi kukhulisa \"kutfula\" kwatehlisa. Lelicembu ligcizelela kutsi loku kukhombisa emasimo emitsi lasebentako, lakhandza simo sekutiphatsa, hhayi bufakazi bemuva lokutiva ngekwemuntfu ngamunye.",
  "Architecting Trust in Artificial Epistemic Agents": "Architecting Trust in Artificial Epistemic Agents",
  "Argues that ontology — once dismissed as impractical — has become load-bearing infrastructure for AI reliability: large language model hallucination exposed a missing layer of \"meaning,\" and pragmatic, embedded ontologies now function as guardrails that anchor probabilistic output to accountable action.": "Isho kutsi i-ontholoji — leyake yasulwa ngekutsi ayisebenti — seyibe siseko lesibalulekile sekwetsemba kwe-AI: kucabanga lokungakalungi kwemamodeli lamakhulu elulwimi kwaveta luhlaka loluphutseleko lwe\"nchazo,\" futsi ema-ontholoji lasebentiswako, lafakwe ngekhatsi manje asebenta njengetivikelo letiboshelela imiphumela yematfuba etentweni letinesibopho.",
  "Artificial Intelligence and Legal Personhood: Ethical, Regulatory, and Accountability Challenges in Contemporary Jurisprudence": "Artificial Intelligence and Legal Personhood: Ethical, Regulatory, and Accountability Challenges in Contemporary Jurisprudence",
  "Artificial Persons": "Bantfu Labentiwe Ngekwe-AI",
  "At the UN’s inaugural Global Dialogue on AI Governance in Geneva, Secretary-General António Guterres called for coordinated worldwide rules covering everything from child-safety obligations on AI developers to limits on unsafe autonomous weapons, warning that unchecked AI could deepen inequality between rich and poor nations.": "Kuncoco lwekucala lwe-UN Global Dialogue on AI Governance eGeneva, uNobhala-Jenerali António Guterres ubite imitsetfo lehlanganisiwe yemhlaba wonkhe lehlanganisa konkhe kusuka etibophweni tekuvikela bantfwana kubadali be-AI kuya emikhawulweni yetikhali letitiphatsako letingephephile, ecwayisa kutsi i-AI lengalawulwa ingaphindzisela kungalingani emkatsini wetive letifuyene naletingafuyene.",
