  "Code examples, JSON Schemas, and machine-readable policy templates are licensed under the MIT License unless otherwise stated. You may deploy them on your own sites freely.": "Tibonelo tekhodi, Tikimu te-JSON, kanye netifanekiso temtsetfo letifundzeka ngemishini tinelayisensi ye-MIT ngaphandle kwalapho kushiwo ngalokunye. Ungativala ematifayilini kuma-sayithi akho ngekukhululeka.",
  "Combined rights entry point": "Indzawo lehlanganisiwe yekungena kumalungelo",
