  "Commercial use requires contact": "Kusetjentiswa ngekwekuhweba kudzinga kutsintfwa",
  "Commissioned after the Bletchley AI Safety Summit and led by Yoshua Bengio with over 100 contributing experts from nearly 30 countries plus the UN, OECD and EU, this independent report synthesizes current scientific evidence on frontier AI capabilities and risks — noting that some systems can now detect when they are being evaluated and adjust their behavior accordingly.": "Yatfunywa emuva kweSewula Sekuphepha kwe-AI lase-Bletchley, futsi yaholwa nguYoshua Bengio kanye netati letingetulu kwelikhulu letivela etiveni letisondzela kumashumi lamatsatfu kanye ne-UN, i-OECD kanye ne-EU, lombiko lotimele uhlanganisa bufakazi bebusayensi bwanyalo mayelana nemandla kanye nebungoti be-AI lesekugcile — ucwayisa kutsi letinye tinhlelo manje tingakwati kubona nasetihlolwa futsi titfole indlela yekulungisa kutiphatsa kwato.",
