  "Learning depth: indexing, embedding, fine-tuning, training, distillation": "Bunzulu bekufundza: kubekwa ngendzawo, i-embedding, kulungisa lokucophelela, kufundzisa, kucindzetela",
  "Learning-permission semantics are the hardest to verify technically — AILP declares intent, it cannot yet prove compliance.": "Umchazo wemvumo yekufundza nguwo lomatima kucinisekiswa ngebuchwepheshe — i-AILP imemetela inhloso, ayikakwati kucinisekisa kuhambisana.",
