  "Legal recognition of learning permissions varies by jurisdiction and is unresolved.": "Kwemukelwa ngekwemtsetfo kwemvumo yekufundza kuyehluka ngekwemkhakha wemtsetfo futsi akukacatjulwa.",
  "Let publishers stay maximally open at shallow levels while reserving deep levels (training, redistribution).": "Vumela bashiceleli bahlale bevulekile kakhulu emazingeni lamancane ngesikhatsi babekela eceleni emazinga lanzulu (kufundzisa, kusakata kabusha).",
