  "Turns declared rights into executable licensing: quote, pay, verify, audit, revoke.": "Guculani emalungelo lamenyetelwe abe kunikwa kwelayisensi lokusebentako: intengo, khokha, cinisekisa, hlola, hoxisa.",
  "Twenty languages live in total: English, Traditional Chinese, Simplified Chinese, Japanese, Korean, French, German, Spanish, Portuguese, Russian, Arabic, Turkish, Persian, Bengali, Hindi, Indonesian, Vietnamese, Greek, Italian, Dutch.": "Emalulwimi lamashumi lamabili asetjentiswa sewonkhe: siNgisi, siChina Lesidzala, siChina Lelula, siJapani, siKorea, siFulentji, siJalimane, siSpanish, siPutukezi, siRussia, siArabhu, siTurkey, siPheshiya, siBengali, siHindi, siIndonesia, siVietnam, siGrikhi, siNtaliyane, siDutch.",
  "Two license tiers: a free public tier and a contact-based commercial tier.": "Emabanga lamabili elayisensi: libanga levulekile lemphakatsi mahhala kanye nelibanga lekuhweba lelisekelwe kutsintfana.",
  "UI": "I-UI",
  "Undefined openness reads as legal uncertainty to AI pipelines and gets cleaned out; only protocolized, machine-readable permission makes content genuinely learnable.": "Kuvuleka lokungachaziwe kufundzwa njengekungacaci kwemtsetfo etindleleni te-AI futsi kuyahlanjululwa; imvumo lehlelwe ngetiphrothokholi, lefundzeka ngemishini, kuphela yiyona lentela lokucuketfwe kufundzeleke ngempela.",
  "Usage logs and audit trails": "Tirekhodi tekusetjentiswa kanye netindzawo tekuhlolwa",
