  "“AICL: AI Ingestion & Capability Layer” now published in English as the canonical edition; the Chinese original manuscript remains available and both versions cross-link.": "\"AICL: AI Ingestion & Capability Layer\" nyalo ishicilelwe ngesiNgisi njengevesheni lesemtsetfweni; umbhalo wesiChina wemsuka usasele utfolakala futsi bobabili labo mavesheni bayaxhumana.",
  "“Protocolized Openness” confirmed as an English-language paper (with Chinese parallel passages) — no separate translation planned.": "\"Protocolized Openness\" icinisekisiwe njengeliphepha lelulwimi lwesiNgisi (nemigca lefanako yesiChina) — akukho lokunye kuhunyushwa lokuhleliwe.",
